{"tid":1502229,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"職工盟下周一到國泰城集會　國泰：國泰城屬禁制令涵蓋範圍","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T00:37:37.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f00df5ec6d7f309c112d1451130ff25c2077612","tid":1502229,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1476479_1_L_20190824133028.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1476479_1_L_20190824133028.jpg&h=b2408f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空表示，知悉職工盟計劃星期一下午在國泰城舉行集會活動，公司已提醒員工，機管局已獲批的禁制令亦涵蓋國泰城範圍，又向員工重申，對於任何支持或參與非法示威、暴力或過於激進的行為，均採取零容忍態度。<br />\n<br />\n國泰說，國泰城是公司全球營運總部，當中包括支援航班運作至關重要的設施，任何影響安全營運的活動，不但嚴重阻礙市民出行，亦會對公司的顧客及員工安全造成威脅，同時破壞香港經濟及香港國際機場的聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n國泰重申，公司全力支持維護《基本法》所賦予的一切權利和自由，國泰是一間營運遍佈全球的國際航空公司，必須遵守航班飛往及飛越國家及地區，包括中國內地的所有適用法規。"},{"pid":"a8dc783f95c62509f5913648575f231cbb7c5284","tid":1502229,"uid":198008,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"大罷工啦"},{"pid":"dc4470529e3ce0e68eb8c5b15a18ccb6334cce9d","tid":1502229,"uid":4739,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"工會唔做野，之後唔慌有好日子"},{"pid":"bac17ebaeb3eab0e1528ab548f874215481f0348","tid":1502229,"uid":103759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c440f2cbae0b03176dc385956b804a4d28758da1","tid":1502229,"uid":22585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bac17ebaeb3eab0e1528ab548f874215481f0348","tid":1502229,"uid":103759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"火上加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /